					<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/von-pincier" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1315056); return false;"  ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1315056&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610164629" alt="Von Pincier" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1315056)"/></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/von-pincier" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1315056); return false;" >Von Pincier</a></span> <span class="odate time_1456425026 format_%25e%20%25b%20%25Y%2C%20%25H%3A%25M%7Cagohover">25 Feb 2016 18:30</span>
														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-2463259">
									

<p>Aaaaand here's part 3 of the Notos Blues &amp; Jazz Band Experience's contribution to the <a href="/mobile-task-force-contest">MTF Contest</a>! I'm super happy to be getting back into writing the Orthodoxy, though I do wish I could have included more of those lovely, crunchy technical footnotes.</p>
<p>In case you missed it, I'd recommend reading <a href="/scp-2474">SCP-2474</a> and the <a href="/m13-personnel-memorabilia-log">M13 Personnel Memorabilia Log</a> to get the full story, as it now stands.</p>
<p>Massive thanks are due to my teammates <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/kalinin" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2203795); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2203795&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1456425093" alt="Kalinin" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2203795)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/kalinin" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2203795); return false;">Kalinin</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/minmin" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(560062); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=560062&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1456425093" alt="minmin" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=560062)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/minmin" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(560062); return false;">minmin</a></span> and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/zyn" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1404533); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1404533&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1456425093" alt="Zyn" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1404533)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/zyn" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1404533); return false;">Zyn</a></span>, of course, and also to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/embertech" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2259245); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2259245&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1456425093" alt="EmberTech" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2259245)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/embertech" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2259245); return false;">EmberTech</a></span> for indirectly inspiring the name and helping me translate it.</p>
<p>The Orthodoxy is going to space!</p>

