			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-2464534">
									

<p>I did enjoy it, especially the tone shift where Spline just gets down to brass tracks.</p>
<p>I'm really, really unclear about Spline's logic and motivation at the end, though, and not in a cryptic or exotic way: in a purely textual way. Primary point:</p>
<blockquote>
<p>The point being- remote contact failed. I see no reason why direct contact wouldn't.</p>
</blockquote>
<p>&#8230; no reason why direct contact wouldn't&#8230; fail.</p>
<p>So, double negative, every reason that it would fail. If this is the intended meaning, then I'm missing something.</p>

