<p>7. And in the rays of the golden sun the MEKHANE saw a third sphere, of water and soil, which it had overlooked in its insignificance.<br />
7. And the MEKHANE, seeing its Knowledge would be needed, departed for the final sphere f, and was there Broken for Us.</p>
</blockquote>
<p>Shouldn't the latter be 8?</p>

